                    <h2>What about the Ritz?</h2>
                    <p>Really, you still want to talk about lodging? We do not have a group rate at the Ritz, but you are welcome to stay there and soak your feet in champagne every night. You will be able to reach the Village by gondola until 10 pm.</p>

