                    <p>Definitely, bring your snow gear, skis, boards, mittens and reindeer sleigh. Bring a bathing suit for the hot tub or pool. The wedding itself is a formal affair, in a suits-not-tuxes kind of way. The ceremony will be outside, so please bundle up!</p>

